                shape: BoxShape.circle,
              ),
              child: Center(
                child: Skeletonizer(
                  enabled: true,
                  effect: const ShimmerEffect(
                    baseColor: AppColors.greyLight200,
                    highlightColor: Colors.white,
                    duration: Duration(milliseconds: 1200),
                  ),
                  child: Icon(
                    Icons.credit_card,
                    color: AppColors.primary,
                    size: 40.r,
